items.prompt: a group of nuns singing hymns in the church. The sky emits fluctuating golden light and golden powder falls from the sky. Dressed in traditional black robes and white headscarves, they are neatly arranged in a row with their hands folded in front of their chests. Their expressions are solemn and pious, as if they are conducting some kind of religious ceremony or prayer. The nuns' eyes looked up, showing great concentration and awe, as if they were talking to the gods.
